entries.journal_entry_description: Infiltrate the Blackscale Compound and Send a Call for Lord Cyssc
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: In the heart of the command bunker in the Blackscale Compound you will find the communications center. Get here and access the terminal to send a call for aid to Lord Cyssc on Hss'kor.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Our lord would not have thought to hear such a thing from you Tosk, but your request is granted. Lord Cyssc will make his way to Kashyyyk without delay.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Put for the call to Lord Cyssc.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Gursan Bryes. A warm welcome must be prepared for Lord Cyssc's arrival.
